title: Castlevania: Lords of Shadow - Mirror of Fate HD [Xbox360] [XBLA
description:
Castlevania: Lords of Shadow - Mirror of Fate HD.

Language: English

This Castlevania: Lords of Shadow sequel reveals the story of the Belmont's,
as they battle destiny across generations, to discover their true fate.
Trevor Belmont, knight of the Brotherhood of Light, embarks on an epic
quest to avenge his mother, killed by his father, Gabriel. Once Gabriel
Belmont, now the all powerful Dracula, he declares war on the
Brotherhood, leading to a cataclysmic showdown between Father & Son!
